github.adeo88.groupme.api

Class Member

  • java.lang.Object
    • github.adeo88.groupme.api.Member

  • public class Member
extends java.lang.Object
    A Member represents the GroupMe API Member. A Member belongs to a group and is associated with a specific user_id. The nickname can be different than the account name associated with the user_id. A Member contains a member_id specific to a group of which most calls depend on. Additionally a member can have associated roles assigned to it, such as "owner".
    Author:
    adeo8
